A

add(ConfigurationCoordinate) - Method in class org.microbean.configuration.cdi.annotation.ConfigurationCoordinates.Literal
Adds a ConfigurationCoordinate to this ConfigurationCoordinates.Literal's collection of such coordinates.

C

Configuration - Annotation Type in org.microbean.configuration.cdi.annotation
An annotation—not a Qualifier—identifying a subspace within a larger configuration value space located in overall configuration space by configuration coordinates.
Configuration.Literal - Class in org.microbean.configuration.cdi.annotation
An AnnotationLiteral representing a runtime instance of the Configuration annotation.
ConfigurationCoordinate - Annotation Type in org.microbean.configuration.cdi.annotation
A repeatable annotation representing an individual configuration coordinate in a universe of such coordinates.
ConfigurationCoordinate.Literal - Class in org.microbean.configuration.cdi.annotation
An AnnotationLiteral that implements ConfigurationCoordinate.
ConfigurationCoordinates - Annotation Type in org.microbean.configuration.cdi.annotation
A Qualifier that houses individual ConfigurationCoordinate annotations.
ConfigurationCoordinates.Literal - Class in org.microbean.configuration.cdi.annotation
An AnnotationLiteral that implements ConfigurationCoordinates.
ConfigurationsExtension - Class in org.microbean.configuration.cdi

NULL - Static variable in annotation type org.microbean.configuration.cdi.annotation.ConfigurationValue
A String that stands in for null—annotation elements cannot be set to null so if either the ConfigurationValue.value() or ConfigurationValue.defaultValue() elements in this class return the value of this field it is to be interpreted as if it were actually null.
